Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:10.77,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:36.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami's tales of his younger years taught Asta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,that you'll always find a path \Nas long as you don't give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and Asta's competitive spirit was \Nignited in his rivalry with Yuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:46.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm gonna catch \Nup to Yuno and surpass him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:47.65,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.38,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.98,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno who the hell you are,\N but stop that racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:55.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know that this is the \Nhome of the Black Bulls,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,the Magic Knights Squad that Mister Yami—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.70,0:00:59.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:04.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're Lady Sisgoleon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:37.99,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Formation of the Royal Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:40.26,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1482,1)}Mereoleona Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:42.53,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:45.45,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is the Captain of \Nthe Crimson Lion Kings doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.35,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:50.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! What are you doing here,\N Captain Sisgoleon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:51.90,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mereoleona!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:57.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is all that racket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.63,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even take a dump in pea—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.11,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency! A wild beast \Nhas invaded the premises!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:05.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, leave the base immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Any of you that don't make \Nit out, just play dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:10.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look her in the eye! She'll eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.81,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and accept this, you fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:18.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is this some hellish drink \Nthat'll set my throat ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:21.01,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,and make me spit fire after a single sip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.01,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,It's to thank you for visiting Fuegoleon.\NDo you wanna die for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:28.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:32.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, this drink can't be for humans \Nif someone as violent as you likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:34.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.70,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:38.65,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to kill \Nthe person you're thanking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.67,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you with gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are way too serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:44.36,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I dislike jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:49.55,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want it, Captain? \NThen can I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:55.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. You just came to see Captain Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:04:00.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I totally thought you were gonna \Ntake me someplace awful aga—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.85,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, I might \Nas well take you lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?! \NWhere are you taking us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.72,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hell? Is it hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:14.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No! Wh-Why are you taking me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.02,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Are there strong people where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.99,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving already? But I made tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:25.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Your squad members \Nare being kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.52,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that means you're leaving, have at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.85,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:36.36,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're sacrifices! What the heck \Ndid we do to deserve this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:40.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you guys shoulda \Nbeen better people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.13,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, Luck! Serves you damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:47.18,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,They all passed the \NRoyal Knights Selection Exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.94,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:51.19,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,W-We passed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We made it into the Royal Knights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't win the tournament,\Nbut Yuno didn't leave me behind, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:01.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We can both still strive to become the \NWizard King and fight on the same stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.71,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.72,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I passed! I passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.88,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That means I get to stay with Asta—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.87,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that I actually care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.83,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, I'm happy that Asta passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.26,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,but that's just because he's in \Nthe same squad as me! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.17,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, it'll be great working \Ntogether as fellow Royal Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.11,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:28.43,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go barging in on your own again \Nand cause trouble for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I've been training even harder, \Nso you don't have to worry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:35.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Did you even hear what I said?! \NI said {\i1}don't{\i0} go barging into places!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:40.52,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I believe there's \None other Black Bull who passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:42.78,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? One more?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.90,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? Maybe I'm the \None you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.14,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.28,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.95,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.96,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Right here! Magna Swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.18,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,It's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:56.29,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. \NA summons has been sent to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:59.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I didn't make it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.06,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you, Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.89,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become even stronger \Nin the Royal Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:09.94,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,so I might get too strong for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.81,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up no \Nmatter how many times I fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:22.15,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not crap your pants when you \Ncome back and I'm way stronger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:26.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,All right, training time! \NVanessa, spar with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:29.71,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I'm about to enjoy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:33.74,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get stronger! I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:39.07,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine. I guess I'll just have my \Nfun later, you virgin delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.50,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a delinquent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:46.51,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be ready, Luck! \NSo... come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:48.26,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.80,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:52.30,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.62,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be cheering you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.68,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm loving the looks on their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.71,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Go kick some ass.
