Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.70,top,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,My name always sounds so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.87,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,From the Blue Rose Knights, Puli Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:25.63,sign_10111_106_Venue_for_the_Ro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Member of the Blue Rose Knights, 4th Class Senior Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Puli Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:25.63,top,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here! Did you all miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.20,top,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,From the Green Praying Mantises, En Ringard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:30.15,sign_10111_106_Venue_for_the_Ro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1,785)}Member of the Green Praying Mantises, 4th Class Senior Magic Knight\N{\fs30}En Ringard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:32.76,top,Mush,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah! Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.64,main,En,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:38.16,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1,787)}Captain of the Aqua Deer\N{\fs30}Rill Boismortier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:40.12,top,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,From the Aqua Deer, Captain Rill \NBoismortier and Fragil Tormenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:42.90,sign_10111_106_Venue_for_the_Ro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(757,772)}Member of the Aqua Deer Squad, 3rd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Fragil Tormenta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.98,top,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. I'm Rill, the Magic Knights Squad captain \Nwho couldn't even win the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.15,main,Fragil,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, please get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:54.87,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,From the Golden Dawn, Hamon Caseus, \NKlaus Lunettes, Mimosa Vermillion, and Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.07,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.07,0:08:00.50,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Member of the Golden Dawn, 2nd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Hamon Caseus
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:00.50,top,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,More candidates were chosen \Nfrom our squad than any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:04.75,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Member of the Golden Dawn, 3rd Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Klaus Lunettes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:04.75,top,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we call Golden Dawn \Nquality and Golden Dawn pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:08.52,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1,783)}Member of the Golden Dawn, 5th Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Yuno
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:10.36,top,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Of course Yuno was chosen! \NHe was the MVP of the Selection Exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:12.26,sign_11720_132_Bell_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(710,1)}Bell
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.26,top,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:17.76,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,From the Black Bulls, \NLuck Voltia, Noelle Silva, and Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.26,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:23.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,How you like that, Yuno?! \NI didn't get left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:25.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up, \Nno matter how many times I fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll fall again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.70,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,You do nothing but fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whenever I get a chance..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What the hell, man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.74,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just stating the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:36.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and the part where I keep \Ngetting back up is true, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.24,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he accepted the falling part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:42.50,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Member of the Golden Dawn, 5th Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs30}Mimosa Vermillion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:42.50,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that I get to \Nwork with you again, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.70,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late in introducing myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:51.00,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm Mereoleona Vermillion, \Nand I've been appointed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.84,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,the Captain of the Royal Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:57.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Lady Sisgoleon's the \NCaptain of the Royal Knights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:59.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why's no one else surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.15,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that'd be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.98,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,She just did roll call, and she's \Nthe one who came to get us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.31,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:18.37,sign_13177_157_1st_Class_Interm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}1st Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs15}Nils Ragus
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:18.37,sign_13177_158_4th_Class_Senior,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}4th Class Senior Magic Knight\N{\fs15}Ben Benfunk
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:18.37,sign_13177_159_1st_Class_Interm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}1st Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs15}Ruben Shagger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:12.43,top,ruben,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is she leading our \NCrimson Lion Kings Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:16.73,top,ruben,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Mereoleona's also royalty!\N Who could be more fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.37,top,Ben,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.04,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I would've preferred
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:23.46,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,that our captain of the Golden Dawn, \NCaptain Vangeance, be chosen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.75,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,but he's busy leading the troops guarding \Nthe royal capital, so this'll have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.78,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,If any of you have any objections, \Ndon't hold back! State them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:32.65,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I also won't hold back in crushing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.27,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:40.30,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! You sixteen survived \Nthe brutal Selection Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:43.14,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,and were chosen to become Royal Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.62,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,If there are no objections,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.58,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,from this day until we annihilate \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.65,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,your lives will be in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.07,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.65,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.55,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,One of you is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.70,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Is he disrespecting me by being late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:02.16,main,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,My bad! Guess I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.17,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,So you {\i1}are{\i0} disrespecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:20.96,main,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see how strong you were,\Nsince my life's going to be in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:23.18,main,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why the heck are you wearing that robe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:42.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why the heck are you \Nwearing a Black Bulls robe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:46.66,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbass. It's because I'm a member \Nof the Black Bulls, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.59,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the Black Bulls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.92,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.75,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bittersweet memory from years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:05.01,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I was kicking the asses of some \NMagic Knights due to reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:08.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights?! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:11.81,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. I said I had reasons, you little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:16.16,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, while I was doing that, \NI ran into this terrible monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.78,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,and he ended up kicking my ass instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.99,flashback,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.53,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.54,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty fun, so you can have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.75,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You can toss it if you don't want it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.10,flashback,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Quit messing with me, you crazy Magic Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.86,flashback,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd ever wear—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.84,flashback,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't just hand these out like candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:44.09,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,See? You do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:48.29,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you can just put it \Non whenever you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.47,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,So, yeah, that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:59.40,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Yami scouted me, and I got into the \NMagic Knights through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck, Xerx?! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.78,sign_17323_210_Also_got_in_thro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Also got in through\N the back door
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what \NI went through to get in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:07.24,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'm not Xerx.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.81,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Zora Ideale, \Nyou shitty little junior shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.00,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What the heck is a Zora?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your real name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.81,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I just told you it was, you stupid shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:19.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did you lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.14,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.64,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to fool your enemies, \Nyou need to fool your friends first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:27.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What enemies?! And wait, \Nare you my senior, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.64,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Damn straight. Show me some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck no! And you need to \Napologize for a lot of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name again? Zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the heck is going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.69,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy, you shitty little shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, what the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:45.86,italics,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start working toward it now. Not a \Nsuper mage, but a true Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:49.75,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Have another rainbow stink bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:56.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a raging stench!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it smells kinda okay \Nonce you get used to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,It absolutely does not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It reeks like no other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:06.68,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you should fight me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:10.41,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna keep yapping, \Nyou impudent little fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:14.09,main,asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd everyone else go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.79,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,They went to change into their \NRoyal Knights robes ages ago, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Royal Knights robes, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:23.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that \Nsuper-cool-sounding thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:26.81,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,They were created for our fight against
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:29.88,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,the Eye of the Midnight Sun, \Nwith high resistance to magic attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go change!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.79,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.48,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.26,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he just the handsomest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.21,main,Bell,0000,0000,0000,,I think I fell in love all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:45.30,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew a day would come when \Nwe'd be wearing the same robes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.77,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But we're not on the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:51.43,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll become the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.71,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.27,0:14:00.15,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it looks like \Nyou've all finished changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:07.59,main,Kirsch,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful. Why do I look \Nso good in everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:11.03,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, you're so narcissistic \Nthat it's making me ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:13.16,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,This is so exhilarating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:17.53,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,It fits so nicely, even on us heftier folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.42,main,Puli,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo! I'm so pumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.50,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess it's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why's mine so short?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.05,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that robe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.15,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, why are you joking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:33.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! This is how it \Nlooked when I put it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.40,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Guess the half-baked twit \Nalso gets just half a robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:44.57,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We ran out of fabric because we \Ngot a few additional members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.74,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Additional members?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.44,0:14:54.49,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't take the exam, but they \Nare essential to making this plan work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:58.50,sign_21447_269_Mage_Attendant_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Mage Attendant to the Wizard King\N{\fs24}Cob Portaport
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:58.50,sign_21447_270_1st_Class_Interm,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}1st Class Intermediate Magic Knight\N{\fs24}Shiren Tium
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.75,top,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Shiren Tium and Cob Portaport.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:02.71,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Shiren's stone creation magic can \Ncreate models of the enemy's base
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:06.25,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,and measure the magic \Nlevels of the mages there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.01,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Cob has very convenient spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:15.01,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,He has been added because Finral Roulacase \Nis still recovering from his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.02,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,And one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:22.02,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Captain of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nozel Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:22.02,top,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel Silva! He will be joining us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.48,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:27.12,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain of the Silver Eagles?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.75,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't ask for better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:33.99,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! I get to \Nfight alongside my captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:39.05,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd decline. \NWhat brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:44.00,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear anything from you. \NI'm only here because the king ordered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:49.26,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You lot, along with these three,\N are the Royal Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:52.36,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hey, Nozel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.71,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you just show up \Nlike it's no big deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:58.73,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't even take the exam!\N That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:03.19,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,What I want to know is, why did {\i1}you{\i0} bother \Ntaking the exam when you're a captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.27,main,Rill,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I could've joined \Nwithout even taking the exam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:13.30,sign_6730_49_Captain_of_the_A,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(656,751)}King of the Clover Kingdom\N{\fs30}Augustus Kira Clover XIII
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.87,top,King,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun\N is a fearsome enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:15.41,top,King,0000,0000,0000,,The aid of a Magic Knights Squad captain,\Nparticularly a royal one, will be essential!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:19.01,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats royalty! \NIt's all about us royals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:25.08,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Your Majesty, \NKing Augustus Kira Clover XIII.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.66,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,She's so fierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:31.16,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember the last time \Nanyone used my full name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:35.49,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well, men! Don't do \Nanything to bring shame upon—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:39.07,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,I think you all know this, but we have \Nno use for anything other than victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.44,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.98,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,a terrorist organization that \Nthreatens the Clover Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:48.02,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't take care of them ourselves, \Nthere will never be peace in our land!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.99,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,You all worked together when \Nthey attacked the royal capital
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.65,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,and were successful in eliminating them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.53,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,but there were still severe consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:59.16,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,My foolish younger brother Fuegoleon \Nfell at the enemy's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.29,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,and he has still not awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.99,0:17:05.50,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,What we learned from the agents \Nwe captured is that their leader
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:09.84,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,is a mage with a four leaf\N clover grimoire, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:13.80,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We learned that they have an upper \Nechelon called the Third Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.27,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,And that, for reasons unknown,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.27,0:17:20.04,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,they are collecting magic \Nstones in order to be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:25.03,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,reborn in their true forms \Nand obtain great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.81,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,There are only three magic stones left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:31.29,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to obtain two of \Nthem before they got to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:36.11,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We were also able to defeat Vetto,\Nthe Third Eye's user of beast magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.70,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,as well as Fana, who commanded Salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:44.16,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,The remaining member of the Third Eye\N is a user of copy magic, Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:51.26,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that Raia and Licht will \Nbe our strongest opponents in this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:55.42,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to be attacking \Ntheir stronghold,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.01,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,so our enemy will do everything \Nthey can to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.56,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Some of us may fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:03.10,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,but we will be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.85,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to give our all in this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:08.46,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Any fools who fail to do so will be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.61,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,taken out by me before we even \Nget to the enemy's stronghold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.01,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.36,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.49,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, King Augustus Kira Clover XIII!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:21.16,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you yelling at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.96,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue what you were saying earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:31.17,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,You're ordering me to continue the conversation \Nwhen you already said everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:34.67,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely nothing else left to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.72,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Well, do good work out there. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:41.69,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:50.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Where is the Eye of the \NMidnight Sun's hideout, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:54.54,italics,King,0000,0000,0000,,A good question, even though \Nhe's an infuriating little peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:55.92,main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:59.34,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,The Eye of the Midnight Sun's hideout
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.16,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,is located in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:07.33,sign_10111_106_Venue_for_the_Ro,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(731,1477)}Strong Magic Region "Gravito Stones"\N{\fs30}Floating Dungeon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:06.18,top,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,a floating dungeon within the strong \Nmagic region known as Gravito Stones!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:19.97,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'm pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.44,flashback,Elf luck,0000,0000,0000,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:24.95,flashback,Elf Char,0000,0000,0000,,I see you look as moronic as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.95,0:19:29.09,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that. \NLet's have a drink sometime, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.14,flashback,Elf char,0000,0000,0000,,I decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:32.68,flashback,Elf luck,0000,0000,0000,,He is pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:37.15,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.63,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, Raia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.99,flashback,Elf rill,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.61,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Are you too lazy to even wake up nowadays?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.61,0:19:45.87,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.24,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:53.00,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Patry. Hogging the \Nspot next to Licht again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:56.63,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,After tomorrow's ceremony, \Nhe's going to belong to someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.91,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,so you should probably cut the cord soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:02.49,flashback,Patry,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. I can do what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:03.91,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,What, you little brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:08.28,flashback,Tetia,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Even if I marry Licht, \Nhe still belongs to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:11.02,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,The human princess sure is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:14.27,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,That kindness is going to \Ncause you trouble someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:18.11,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that space is gonna \Nbe gone sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:22.57,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Stop picking on him. Patry knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:26.66,flashback,Fana,0000,0000,0000,,So, Licht, how does it feel, knowing you're\N going to be a father in a few months?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:30.24,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel the mana blessing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:35.26,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very happy our child will come into \Nthis world welcomed by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.30,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This child is our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.22,flashback,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It'll bridge the gap between elves and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.84,flashback,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Licht and Tetia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.22,flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.92,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about a fleeting dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.70,main,Raia,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the awakening must be near.
