Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:36.77,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:41.04,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}All Kinds of Robes\NPart 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:41.04,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,All Kinds of Robes, Part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.04,0:22:44.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Royal police robes, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:46.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that \Nsuper-cool-sounding thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.58,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,They're robes made to \Nexcel in investigations!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:51.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go change!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:58.68,sign_32950_385_Halt_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Halt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.63,0:22:58.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't even robes! \NWait, why is mine so different?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.40,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,All Kinds of Robes\NPart 2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.40,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Part 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:03.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Royal school robes, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.73,0:23:06.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that \Nsuper-cool-sounding thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:09.36,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,They're robes made to excel in academic life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:10.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go change!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:16.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Again, why is mine so different?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:18.12,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,All Kinds of Robes\NPart 3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:18.12,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Part 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.12,0:23:21.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Royal doctor robes, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.66,0:23:24.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is that \Nsuper-cool-sounding thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:27.48,main,Mere,0000,0000,0000,,They're robes made to excel \Nin emergency medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:29.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go change!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.50,0:23:35.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! Why is mine the \Nonly one that's different?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:37.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:42.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time to fight \Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:46.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Royal Knights, are going to protect \Nthe Clover Kingdom and its people!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:50.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 88: \N"Storming the Eye of the Midnight Sun's Hideout!!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 88\N\N{\fs18} Storming the Eye of the Midnight Sun's Hideout!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:54.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Sisgoleon's strong! Super strong!
